Jahking Guillory (born 2001) is an American actor, best known for his starring role in the 2016 film, Kicks.  Guillory appears in The Chi on Showtime, and the Netflix series On My Block as Latrelle.
He was born and grew up in Long Beach, California. In 2025, Guillory enlisted in the United States Marine Corps out of Moreno Valley, California.
